{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparisons-with-the-logical-or-operator","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Poredjenja sa Logickim OR Operatorom","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><dfn>Logicki OR</dfn> operator (<code>||</code>) vraca <code>true</code> ako je makar jedan od <dfn>operanada</dfn> <code>true</code>. U suprotnom vraca <code>false</code>.</p>\n<p><dfn>Logicki OR</dfn> operator ima dve uspravne crte: (<code>||</code>). Obicno se nalazi izmedju tastera Backspace i Enter.</p>\n<p>Primer ispod bi trebalo da vam bude poznat iz prethodnih lekcija.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">if (num > 10) {\n  return \"No\";\n}\nif (num &#x3C; 5) {\n  return \"No\";\n}\nreturn \"Yes\";\n</code></pre>\n<p>Ovaj kod ce vratiti <code>Yes</code> ako je <code>num</code> izmedju <code>5</code> i <code>10</code> (ukljucujuci <code>5</code> i <code>10</code>). Ista logika moze se zapisati koristeci <dfn>logicki OR</dfn> operator.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">if (num > 10 || num &#x3C; 5) {\n  return \"No\";\n}\nreturn \"Yes\";\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244d9","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Spojite dva <code>if</code> iskaza u jedan koji vraca string <code>Outside</code> ako <code>val</code> nije izmedju <code>10</code> i <code>20</code>, ukljucujuci granice. U suprotnom, vratite string <code>Inside</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":16800,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparisons-with-the-logical-or-operator"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function testLogicalOr(val) {\n  // Only change code below this line\n\n  if (val) {\n    return \"Outside\";\n  }\n\n  if (val) {\n    return \"Outside\";\n  }\n\n  // Only change code above this line\n  return \"Inside\";\n}\n\ntestLogicalOr(15);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Treba da koristite operator <code>||</code> jednom</p>","testString":"assert(__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/\\|\\|/g).length === 1);"},{"text":"<p>Treba da imate samo jedan <code>if</code> iskaz</p>","testString":"assert(__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/if/g).length === 1);"},{"text":"<p><code>testLogicalOr(0)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Outside</code></p>","testString":"assert(testLogicalOr(0) === 'Outside');"},{"text":"<p><code>testLogicalOr(9)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Outside</code></p>","testString":"assert(testLogicalOr(9) === 'Outside');"},{"text":"<p><code>testLogicalOr(10)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Inside</code></p>","testString":"assert(testLogicalOr(10) === 'Inside');"},{"text":"<p><code>testLogicalOr(15)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Inside</code></p>","testString":"assert(testLogicalOr(15) === 'Inside');"},{"text":"<p><code>testLogicalOr(19)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Inside</code></p>","testString":"assert(testLogicalOr(19) === 'Inside');"},{"text":"<p><code>testLogicalOr(20)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Inside</code></p>","testString":"assert(testLogicalOr(20) === 'Inside');"},{"text":"<p><code>testLogicalOr(21)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Outside</code></p>","testString":"assert(testLogicalOr(21) === 'Outside');"},{"text":"<p><code>testLogicalOr(25)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Outside</code></p>","testString":"assert(testLogicalOr(25) === 'Outside');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#basic-javascript","dashedName":"comparisons-with-the-logical-or-operator","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-javascript","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/introducing-else-statements","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparisons-with-the-logical-and-operator","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244d9","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum) {\n  if (endNum - startNum === 0) {\n    return [startNum];\n  } else {\n    const numbers = rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum - 1);\n    numbers.push(endNum);\n    return numbers;\n  }\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparisons-with-the-logical-or-operator"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}